''' <summary> ''' Validates an MPAN number ''' </summary> ''' <param name="mpan">At least the last 13 digits from the MPAN number, including the check digit, ''' expressed as a string</param> ''' <returns>True for valid, otherwise false</returns> ''' <remarks>Written by Martin Milan, May 2012, avoiding use of VB6 compatibility library, for .Net 4.0 Client Profile</remarks> Public Function MPANIsValid(mpan As String) As Boolean
